ward is best value. The Government reserves the right to award without discussions to the offeror that represents best value to the Government.  The associated North American Industrial Classification System (NAICS) code for this procurement is 423450 Medical, Dental, and Hospital Equipment and Supplies Merchant Wholesalers.

